Module instructions
Package fr.project.instructions.simple

Class MyClass

java.lang.Object
fr.project.instructions.simple.MyClass
public class MyClass
extends java.lang.Object
A class that represents a class of a .class file. It contains methods that allow to dectect and write fields and methods of the class.
Author:
CHU Jonathan
